      "text": [
        " : \"إِنَّ اَلْجَدَّ شَرِيكُ اَلْإِخْوَةِ وَ حَظُّهُ مِثْلُ حَظِّ أَحَدِهِمْ مَا بَلَغُوا كَثُرُوا أَوْ قَلُّوا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5641 - Hammad narrated from Hariz from Al-Fuḍayl or someone else from Abu Abdullah (as) who said: \"The grandfather shares the inheritance with the siblings, and his share is equal to the share of one of them, regardless of whether they are many or few.\""
        ]
      }
